se traditions.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aDevelopmental psychology. 0aPsychology, Religious. 0aTranspersonal psychology. 4aPsychology : Jung. 4aPsychology : Psychology of Religion. 4aPsychology : Transpersonal Psychology. 4aReligion and Spirituality : Spirituality. 7aRELIGION / Psychology of Religion.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9780791486269?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780791486269423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780791486269/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles